  "prompt": "Which cheat codes are available for Brave Frontier, and what do they do?",
  "response": "In \"Brave Frontier,\" there are several cheat codes that players can utilize to enhance their gameplay experience. These codes often provide rewards such as free items, units, or resources. However, please note that cheat codes can change over time and may not always be applicable to all versions or updates of the game. \n\nHere are some common types of cheat codes and their typical effects:\n\n1. **Unit Unlock Codes**: These codes can unlock specific rarity units or special event characters.\n   \n2. **Item Codes**: These codes typically grant players valuable in-game items like potions, crystals, or equipment.\n\n3. **Currency Codes**: Players can receive bonuses such as Zelphe (in-game currency), gem rewards, or other resources.\n\n4. **Boost Codes**: These may provide temporary boosts to experience gained, drop rates, or other gameplay mechanics.\n\nTo find specific codes, players usually check community forums, the official game website, or social media pages dedicated to \"Brave Frontier.\" Always be cautious when using third-party sources for codes, as some may not be legitimate or could risk your account security. \n\nFor the most accurate and updated cheat codes, please refer to the game's official channels or fan communities dedicated to \"Brave Frontier.\"",
